Welcome back to Dry Powder. I=E2=80=99m Bill Cohan,
recently returned from R=C3=A9flexion Charlevoix in the rugged, mountainous=
 terrain of northeastern Quebec, where I was celebrating my 65th birthday.

Before getting into the bulk of tonight=E2=80=99s issue=E2=80=94a survey of=
 seasoned Wall Street executives on the first lunatic month of Trump II=E2=
=80=94a few observations from my trip up north. First, I highly recommend R=
