DYxN2RhNDJhYmQxMmEiLCJsaW5rX2lkIjoyMDkxMTI2fQ/a149311444ace2a3f61ee3aac782b=
9a644031cd2268bb313f64ff12b4add630a" style=3D"text-decoration:
underline;color:#d40000;">post</a> on Tuesday, Haass confided that he used =
to be a Democrat, then became a Republican, then decided to have no party a=
ffiliation. (=E2=80=9CI could not rejoin the Democratic Party, as, with few=
 exceptions, it had become a collection of special interests mostly rooted =
in identity politics,=E2=80=9D he wrote.)</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bo=
ttom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Now, without =
a tribe, he finds himself struggling a bit to conceptualize a
coordinated response to Trump beyond MAGA servility or liberal hysteria. =
=E2=80=9CThere has to be a better response than emulating the ostrich and b=
urying your head in the sand in the hope it will blow over,=E2=80=9D he wro=
te. =E2=80=9CNor is indiscriminate opposition the answer, as certain Trump =
initiatives arguably deserve support and, in any event, should be judged on=
 their merits.=E2=80=9D He enumerated the parts of Trump=E2=80=99s agenda, =
in his view, that are worthy of serious consideration, including =E2=80=9Cr=
ooting out actual waste
and fraud in the government, phasing out a penny that costs more to make th=
an it=E2=80=99s worth, making girls=E2=80=99 and women=E2=80=99s sports saf=
e and competitive for girls and women, rolling back questionable aspects of=
 D.E.I., enacting return-to-office policies, and tightening immigration law=
s and their enforcement.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px=
;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">On the other hand, Ha=
ass wrote, criticism and resistance are called for when it comes to pardoni=
ng the
January 6 convicts, firing inspectors general and career prosecutors, shutt=
ing down USAID (this one has been debatable among the Wall Street crowd, as=
 I=E2=80=99ve <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVD=
J4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dWSVBueDZ3c200Y3NQcFdpYnRkND0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wd=
WNrLm5ld3Mvd2FsbC1zdHJlZXQtaXMtc3RpbGwtYWJvYXJkLXRoZS10cnVtcC10cmFpbi8_dXRt=
X2NhbXBhaWduPURyeStQb3dkZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjgyJTJGMTklMkYyNSUyOVx1MDA=
yNnV0bV9jb250ZW50PURyeStQb3dkZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjgyJTJGMTYlMkYyNSUyOV=
x1MDAyNnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWxfYWN0aW9uXHUwMDI2dXRtX3NvdXJjZT1jdXN0b21lci5pb=
1x1MDAyNnV0bV90ZXJtPWY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiZjZjNjA2MTdk=
YTQyYWJkMTJhIiwibGlua19pZCI6MjA3MDgwOX0/684daebb20808d8dac83d4bf1af14efe453=
43fd209a6c40a5d10010675d09454" style=3D"text-decoration:underline;color:#d4=
0000;">noted</a>), calling for an end to birthright citizenship (being adju=
dicated in the courts), withdrawing security details from former government=
 officials, freezing funds already appropriated by Congress, and nominating=
 for
cabinet positions people better suited to a <em>Star Wars</em> bar scene. A=
nd that=E2=80=99s to say nothing of the imperialist posturing regarding Gaz=
a, Greenland, Panama, and Canada.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px=
;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">Haass urged Americans to come up with m=
eaningful alternatives to Trump=E2=80=99s thrusts, not just criticisms. (A =
much harder task, it=E2=80=99s true.) =E2=80=9CIf you don=E2=80=99t like Tr=
ump=E2=80=99s Gaza initiative, and there is good reason not to, then spell =
out what you are prepared
to support, and why that proposal would be a superior alternative,=E2=80=9D=
 he wrote. =E2=80=9CMake the case for foreign assistance and an improved US=
AID. Suggest how the NIH and other recipients of federal funds could be str=
eamlined and made more efficient, as you illustrate how Trump=E2=80=99s pro=
posed cuts could devastate critical, ongoing research into cures for deadly=
 diseases.=E2=80=9D</p></div>
